40
00:10:13,963 --> 00:10:16,555
If you're being chased by someone bad,

41
00:10:16,733 --> 00:10:18,925
I'll call the police.

42
00:10:33,650 --> 00:10:35,315
Put your clothes on.

43
00:10:38,254 --> 00:10:40,145
Please help me.

44
00:11:04,113 --> 00:11:06,045
I just can't live...

45
00:11:06,249 --> 00:11:08,675
